keyMappings:
unmapAll

map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map h scrollLeft
map l scrollRight
map T Vomnibar.activateInNewTab
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map B Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map ñ LinkHints.activateMode
map Ñ LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map <A-ñ> LinkHints.activateMode action=hover
map <C-ñ> LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
map i focusInput
map / enterFindMode
map , performFind
map ; performBackwardsFind

map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom

map { goPrevious
map } goNext

map <C-o> passNextKey
map <A-v> enterVisualMode
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia

g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
d: https://drive.google.com/drive/search?q=%s Drive
m: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Google maps

y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
a: https://aniwave.to/filter?keyword=%s AniWave
